b'Professional Achievements'
b' Fellow of The Institute of Electrical and Electronics Engineers, Jan., 1999, with the citation: \xe2\x80\x9cFor contributions to multirate digital signal processing and digital filter banks.\xe2\x80\x9d'
b' Associate Editor, IEEE Transactions on Image Processing, 1998\xe2\x80\x932000.'
b' Associate Editor, IEEE Signal Processing Letters, 1993\xe2\x80\x931998.'
b' Editorial Board Member of Journal of Visual Communication and Image Representation, 1989\xe2\x80\x931993.'
b' Associate Editor, IEEE Transactions on Circuits & Systems, 1987\xe2\x80\x931989.'
b' Conference Chair of SPIE/IEEE Conference on Visual Communication and Image Processing, jointly with M. J. T. Smith, Orlando, FL, Mar. 1996.'
b' Radiological Soc. of North America, Certificate of Merit for exhibit on medical image compression research, 1994.'
b' Bellcore President\xe2\x80\x99s Recognition Award, Orator speech synthesizer research, 1993.'
b'Research Interests'
b'Professor Ansari\xe2\x80\x99s primary research interest is in signal processing and communications. Topics of research include image and video processing, layered video compression and packetized transmission, multi-modal signal analysis, multirate filter banks and wavelets, and speech processing.'
